From 1bffb0f0ba87ea687029ece303781675ce629ba1 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Amit Mahajan <Amit.Mahajan@windriver.com>
Date: Thu, 16 Jul 2026 11:21:57 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] Add nf_tables fallback for OVS agent kernel module init
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

The neutron-openvswitch-agent-kernel-modules init container runs
modprobe ip6_tables before starting the OVS agent. On kernels that
have moved to nftables-only (6.18.15+deb13-amd64 on Debian Trixie),
the ip6_tables module does not exist — neither as a loadable module
nor as built-in. This causes the init container to fail under
set -ex, triggering CrashLoopBackOff and blocking the entire
libvirt/nova-compute dependency chain, resulting in application
apply failure.

The ip6_tables kernel module is not required on nftables-only
kernels:
- The iptables/ip6tables userspace commands still function via
  the nft_compat kernel module and nf_tables backend
- nf_tables is the unified netfilter framework for both IPv4
  and IPv6

Add a fallback to modprobe nf_tables if ip6_tables is not
available. This maintains backward compatibility with older
kernels (where ip6_tables exists) while supporting newer
nftables-only kernels. If neither module can be loaded, the
script fails fast under set -ex.

Signed-off-by: Amit Mahajan <Amit.Mahajan@windriver.com>
---
 .../bin/_neutron-openvswitch-agent-init-modules.sh.tpl          | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/neutron/templates/bin/_neutron-openvswitch-agent-init-modules.sh.tpl b/neutron/templates/bin/_neutron-openvswitch-agent-init-modules.sh.tpl
index a243867aa..bf868b04a 100644
--- a/neutron/templates/bin/_neutron-openvswitch-agent-init-modules.sh.tpl
+++ b/neutron/templates/bin/_neutron-openvswitch-agent-init-modules.sh.tpl
@@ -15,7 +15,7 @@ limitations under the License.
 */}}
 
 set -ex
-chroot /mnt/host-rootfs modprobe ip6_tables
+chroot /mnt/host-rootfs modprobe ip6_tables || chroot /mnt/host-rootfs modprobe nf_tables
 
 {{- if .Values.conf.ovs_dpdk.enabled }}
 chroot /mnt/host-rootfs modprobe {{ .Values.conf.ovs_dpdk.driver | quote }}
-- 
2.43.0

